main_body:
The Annexe to Regulation (EEC) No 3782/88 is hereby amended as follows:
1. 'Ile d'Oléron' is added to the third indent in point 1;
2. 'Jurançon, Béarn, Irouleguy, Coteaux du Vendomois' is added to the first indent of point 2;
3. 'Pouillon' is added to the names of cantons in the twelfth indent of point 3.
